      "text": [
        " رَجُلٍ أَوْصَى بِثُلُثِ مَالِهِ فِي أَعْمَامِهِ وَ أَخْوَالِهِ فَقَالَ \"لِأَعْمَامِهِ اَلثُّلُثَانِ وَ لِأَخْوَالِهِ اَلثُّلُثُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5483 - Al-Hasan bin Mahbub narrated from Ali bin Ri'ab, from Zurara, from Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) regarding a man who bequeathed one-third of his wealth to his paternal uncles and maternal uncles.\nImam (as) said: \"Two-thirds are for his paternal uncles, and one-third is for his maternal uncles.\""
        ]
      }
    },
